{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 425\u2089 to base 10**\n425\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070\n= 4\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 5\u00d71\n= 324 + 18 + 5\n= 347\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 347\u2089 to base 10**\n347\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070\n= 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 7\u00d71\n= 243 + 36 + 7\n= 286\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n347\u2081\u2080 \u00d7 286\u2081\u2080 = 99,242\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 99,242\u2081\u2080 to base 9**\n99,242 \u00f7 9 = 11,026 R 8 \u2192 Check: 11,026\u00d79 + 8 = 99,242 \u2713\n11,026 \u00f7 9 = 1,225 R 1 \u2192 Check: 1,225\u00d79 + 1 = 11,026 \u2713\n1,225 \u00f7 9 = 136 R 1 \u2192 Check: 136\u00d79 + 1 = 1,225 \u2713\n136 \u00f7 9 = 15 R 1 \u2192 Check: 15\u00d79 + 1 = 136 \u2713\n15 \u00f7 9 = 1 R 6 \u2192 Check: 1\u00d79 + 6 = 15 \u2713\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 R 1 \u2192 Check: 0\u00d79 + 1 = 1 \u2713\n\nRemainders (top to bottom): 8, 1, 1, 1, 6, 1\nReading bottom to top: 161,118\u2089\n\n**Step 5: Verify**\n161,118\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u2075 + 6\u00d79\u2074 + 1\u00d79\u00b3 + 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070\n= 1\u00d759,049 + 6\u00d76,561 + 1\u00d7729 + 1\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 8\u00d71\n= 59,049 + 39,366 + 729 + 81 + 9 + 8\n= 99,242\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n161118", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 680}